netex:CustomerPurchasePackageElementAccess
    a owl:Class ;
    skos:definition "Access to a VALIDABLE ELEMENT by a specific CUSTOMER PURCHASE PACKAGE through use of CUSTOMER PURCHASE PACKAGE. This is needed for validation of complex SALES OFFER PACKAGEs containing tariffs structures that have FARE STRUCTURE ELEMENTs IN SEQUENCE, in such a case a given SALES PACKAGE ELEMENT may have multiple VALIDABLE ELEMENTs associated with it, each of which can be separately validated and marked. +v1.1"@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "access to a validable element"@en ;
